{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/spherecats_title.png?t=1721750440\" /><br>A merge puzzle game in which you combine round cats to make bigger round cats!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/mergegif.gif?t=1721750440\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/classic_mode.png?t=1721750440\" /><br>In classic mode you can play the classic suika/watermelon experience. You drop a cat and, if the cat touches another cat of the same size, they will merge into a larger cat. Try to create the biggest cat possible but, if the cats reach the limit of the container, it will be game over.<br>This is similar to the original suika game, but with a few tweaks in the physics.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/daily_mode.png?t=1721750440\" /><br>In daily variant you play with special rules. <br>Each day there can be up to three special rules such as<strong> low gravity, bouncy cats, time limits</strong>, and more.<br>Play every day to discover them all!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/variant_gif.gif?t=1721750440\" /><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/extras/leaderboards.png?t=1721750440\" /><br>Climb the leaderboard in the classic mode or try to be the star of the day by competing in the daily variant, where a new leaderboard is created every day.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1721750440","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3091310/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=17